    <h1>You have selected Live Entertainment! Here are some great places in Boston to enjoy Live Performances and Sporting Events: </h1>
    <p>This is TD Garden, Boston's main host of concerts for artists of all genres, and sporting events such as Celtics and Bruins games. The massive stadium is located on Legends Way, and is surrounded by many great restuarants such as Tavern in the Square and The Fours for you to grab a meal before you watch a game or a concert. </p>
